         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne 27 October 1853 ¶ My dear Gunn ¶  ¶ I send you the first copy at my disposal of Dr Müllers report upon our Vegetation. ¶  It is one you will read with interest — &amp; admit does him great credi...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">M53.10.27</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Charles La Trobe to Ronald Gunn</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">A249 Gunn correspondence, Mitchell Library, State Library of NSW, Sydney.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne 27 October 1853</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Gunn</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I send you the first copy at my disposal of Dr Müllers report upon our Vegetation.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.1665in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.1665in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B53.10.01.</p>
               </note> It is one you will read with interest — &amp; admit does him great credit. I consider myself very fortunate to have secured to the Colony a man of class and talent — &amp; perseverance —</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>You have now old Mr Swainson — much good may he do you. His report &amp; 'wonderful discover[ies]' are also in the printers hands<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.1665in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.1665in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Swainson (1853).</p>
               </note> — &amp; you shall have them in due time —</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have heard nothing as yet of my successor<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.1665in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.1665in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>La Trobe submitted his resignation as Lieutenant Governor in December 1852 but his successor, Sir Charles Hotham, was not appointed until December 1853 (and did not arrive in Victoria until June 1854).</p>
               </note> —</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Yrs in gt. haste</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>but very truly</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>C. J. Latrobe</p>
         </div>
      </body>
